Souks, spices, colors, beaches, sunshine, and adventure! Morocco! 
•Agafay Desert Day Trip w/ 🐪 ride 10/10 great experience. Our guides were amazing, good food, so much fun, gained a great deal of knowledge & experience 
•Essaouira Day Trip I would definitely do this again with different eyes. This is a day trip where you need to emerge yourself in the hustle & bustle of the culture but hunnnyyy I was tired. The time we took by the water was much needed & I got to have a real heart to heart 💞 with @lipstickcoco
•Marrakesh Dream Ballooning was absolutely amazing! Never been on a hot air balloon & it was so smooth & relaxing. Love that everything included food because we were EATING lol
